This is the Perl module Sub::CharacterProperties.

INSTALLATION

Sub::CharacterProperties installation is straightforward. If your CPAN shell is
set up, you should just be able to do

    % cpan Sub::CharacterProperties

Download it, unpack it, then build it as per the usual:

    % perl Makefile.PL
    % make && make test

Then install it:

    % make install

DOCUMENTATION

Sub::CharacterProperties documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    % perldoc Sub::CharacterProperties

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

